<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title></title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="default.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="overlay-header" id="header">
        <div class="header-top">
            <div class="header-left">
                <span>마법연구회</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="header-center" onclick="toggleInfo()">
                <span id="arrow-icon">▼</span>
            </div>

            <div class="header-right">
                <div class="work-info">
                    <strong>중력시계 (2026)</strong>
                    <span>강지현</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="header-details" id="details">
            <p>시, 분 그리고 초 공을 담는 투명그릇에 1시간, 1분 그리고 1초가 흐를 때 마다 각각의 그릇에 공이 떨어진다. 그리고 백그라운드에는 디지털시계로 시간을 알려주고 있다.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="canvas-container">
        <canvas id="defaultCanvas0"></canvas>
    </main>

    <script>
        function toggleInfo() {
            const header = document.getElementById('header');
            const arrow = document.getElementById('arrow-icon');
            
            header.classList.toggle('is-open');
            
            // 화살표 방향 전환
            if (header.classList.contains('is-open')) {
                arrow.innerText = '▲';
            } else {
                arrow.innerText = '▼';
            }
        }
    </script>

    <a href="page1.html" class="nav-arrow left-arrow">
    <span>&lt;</span>
</a>

<a href="page4.html" class="nav-arrow right-arrow">
    <span>&gt;</span>
</a>
</body>
</html>